name: This is EL VIAJE DE MIS FOTOS
description:
I just came back to Cafayate, Salta with a postcard in my hand.

First I went on 2016 and being there was special.
More special was being there in January of this year 2021.

After print more than 200 postcards of this picture and helping me to keep on travel making money selling it.

My travel was to go far away,
but I realize that being far away makes me come back to places that I already have been.

Here I´m now in the place where I have born: Buenos Aires.
EL VIAJE DE MIS FOTOS is to be just there where I need to be to grow up and keep flying. Now I´m bigger than yesterday and mint this is a new step.

Thanks.
Sincerely,
Juan.
